## What is the purpose of the change

old:
```java

 if (service == null || service.length() == 0) {
            service = parts.length > 0 ? parts[0] : null;
            method = parts.length > 1 ? parts[1] : null;
        } else {
            method = parts.length > 0 ? parts[0] : null;
        }
        if (StringUtils.isInteger(method)) {
            times = method;
            method = null;
        } else {
            times = parts.length > 2 ? parts[2] : "1";
        }
```

Usually we use telnet  in order，first，we invoke ”cd xxxService“ to change the path，then we invoke "trace  xxxMethod 10" to trace a method 。

If we invoke like this "trace  xxxMethod 10" and the service is not equals null（we have changed the path） , times will not change the value  ，It‘s always 1。



